@startuml
title Feature 022 sequence: employee partner card and reports
actor "Сотрудник backoffice" as Employee
actor "Региональный менеджер" as Manager
participant "Frontend web-shell" as FE
participant "EmployeeController" as Controller
participant "EmployeeService" as Service
participant "EmployeeSupportRepository" as Repo
database "employee db" as DB
participant "Order/Claim/Bonus/WMS read models" as ReadModels

Employee -> FE: Открывает /employee/partner-card
FE -> Controller: GET /api/employee/partner-card?query=P-022-7788
Controller -> Service: partnerCard(userContext, query, reason)
Service -> Service: Проверить роль и regional scope
Service -> ReadModels: Получить partner master data, KPI, orders, claims, bonus, WMS flags
ReadModels --> Service: Partner card projection
Service -> Repo: save audit EMPLOYEE_PARTNER_CARD_VIEWED
Repo -> DB: insert employee_partner_card_audit
Service --> Controller: EmployeePartnerCardResponse
Controller --> FE: 200 JSON с KPI, recentOrders, riskSignals, linkedRoutes
FE --> Employee: Показывает карточку партнера

Employee -> FE: Переходит в отчет заказов партнера
FE -> Controller: GET /api/employee/report/order-history?partnerId=PART-022-001&problemOnly=true
Controller -> Service: partnerOrderReport(userContext, filters)
Service -> Service: Проверить фильтры и scope
Service -> ReadModels: Получить историю заказов, claims, payments, delivery, bonus volume
ReadModels --> Service: Items and aggregates
Service -> Repo: save report snapshot and audit EMPLOYEE_PARTNER_REPORT_VIEWED
Repo -> DB: insert employee_partner_report_snapshot
Repo -> DB: insert employee_partner_card_audit
Service --> Controller: EmployeePartnerOrderReportResponse
Controller --> FE: 200 JSON с items, aggregates, appliedFilters, auditRecorded
FE --> Employee: Показывает таблицу и агрегаты

Manager -> FE: Открывает отчет по региональному партнеру
FE -> Controller: GET /api/employee/report/order-history?personNumber=P-022-7788&regionCode=RU-MOW
Controller -> Service: partnerOrderReport(regional-manager, filters)
Service -> Service: Проверить regional manager scope
alt partner вне зоны ответственности
  Service --> Controller: STR_MNEMO_EMPLOYEE_ACCESS_DENIED
  Controller --> FE: 403 EmployeeErrorResponse
else partner доступен
  Service --> Controller: EmployeePartnerOrderReportResponse
  Controller --> FE: 200 JSON
end

Employee -> FE: Открывает связанный order/claim/support route
FE -> Controller: GET /api/employee/partner-card/{partnerId}?supportReasonCode=EMPLOYEE_PARTNER_CARD_LINK_OPENED
Controller -> Service: record partner link context
Service -> Repo: save audit EMPLOYEE_PARTNER_CARD_LINK_OPENED
Repo -> DB: insert employee_partner_card_audit
@enduml